[center][b][size=12pt]Hello everyone, i am Mattias. I have been coding for 7 years. I am equipt with the abilities to write and understand many programming languages. a few being PHP, SQL, Javascript, Java C, C++, C#, and many more. I am in need of dedicated, and friendly staff to help out with this absolutely amazing server i am bringing to the table. This server is very unique, and one of a kind. It is packed with features, and abilities that many of the servers out there respectively lack. If you are interested in joining the team please feel free to add me on skype and contact me there. i will post recruitment dates below![/size][/b][/center]
[center][size=24pt]Recruitment Dates: 06/06/16-06/20/16[/size][/center]
